      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIDNIGHT QUEEN (8) was fast away and led all the way to score two back then gave a start last time but got home into the frame when second at this track (34.97). Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Can find winning form. RITZA KEN (1) was in the minors two back (34.93) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 7th. Form from his last run is proving strong. Warrants plenty of respect. KITTY ANN (2) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (36.45) at Q Lakeside. Has a good record at this journey. Worth following up. PHOENIX AMELIA (4) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this circuit.",
